Interface TableFunction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface TableFunction
    Interface for functions that produce a set of DataSeries derived from an input DataTable.
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman

    • Method Detail

      • getSeries

        void getSeries(List<DataTable> input,
               ListMap<String,DataSeries<?>> outputSeries)
        For the given DataTable produce the series this function generates and add them to the given output list.
        Parameters:
        input - The input DataTable(s). If the series this function generates are not derived from an input table this may be null.
        outputSeries - The ListMap to add the output DataSeries to, key is a label suggestion. One or more DataSeries may be added.
